      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To begin with Chatterbox Python, install the official SDK via pip: "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "pip install chatterbox-sdk",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Ensure Python 3.8+ is used, and set up virtual environments to isolate dependencies. Store API keys in environment variables (e.g., "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "CHATTERBOX_API_KEY",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
